ult | Описание |\n|----------|---------|----------|\n| cdc_enabled | false | Enable CDC |\n| cdc_total_space_in_mb | — | CDC total space |\n| cdc_free_space_check_interval_ms | 250 | Check interval |\n\n### 2.8. Логирование\n\n#### 2.8.1. Logging Configuration\n\n- **Framework**: SLF4J + Logback\n- **Config file**: conf/logback.xml\n- **Package root**: org.apache.cassandra\n\n#### 2.8.2. Log Levels\n\n| Level | Usage |\n|-------|-------|\n| TRACE | Detailed tracing |\n| DEBUG | Query details, compaction debug |\n| INFO | Node lifecycle, schema changes |\n| WARN | Hinted handoff, tombstone warnings |\n| ERROR | Failures, corruption |\n\n#### 2.8.3. Key Log Events\n\n| Level | Event | Pattern |\n|-------|-------|----------|\n| INFO | Node startup | \"Cassandra startup complete\" |\n| INFO | Node join | \"Node /%s is now part of the cluster\" |\n| INFO | Schema change | \"Schema change: %s\" |\n| WARN | Hinted handoff | \"Failed to deliver hint to %s\" |\n| ERROR | CommitLog failure | \"CommitLog exception: %s\" |\n| ERROR | SSTable corruption | \"Corrupt sstable: %s\" |\n\n### 2.9. Валидация входящих значений\n\n| CQL Type | Validation |\n|----------|------------|\n| text | UTF-8 string, max 64KB default |\n| uuid | UUID v1/v4 format |\n| timestamp | ISO-8601 |\n| inet | IP address (IPv4/IPv6) |\n| varint | Arbitrary precision integer |\n| decimal | Arbitrary precision decimal |\n| frozen<> | Immutable collections |\n| counter | Increment-only column |\n\n### 2.10. Обработка ошибок\n\n| Exception | Code | Description |\n|-----------|------|-------------|\n| InvalidRequestException | 0x1000 | CQL syntax/semantic error |\n| NotFoundException | 0x1001 | Row/key not found |\n| UnavailableException | 0x1002 | Not enough replicas available |\n| TimedOutException | 0x1003 | Operation timeout |\n| WriteTimeoutException | 0x1004 | Write didn't complete in time |\n| ReadTimeoutException | 0x1005 | Read didn't complete in time |\n| AlreadyExistsException | 0x1006 | Keyspace/table already exists |\n| UnauthorizedException | 0x1007 | Permission denied |\n| AuthenticationException | 0x1008 | Authentication failed |\n\n### 2.11. Хедеры и метаданные\n\n| Транспорт | Имя | Описание |\n|-----------|-----|----------|\n| CQL | CQL_VERSION | Версия CQL протокола |\n| CQL | CONSISTENCY | Consistency level |\n| CQL | SERIAL_CONSISTENCY | Serial consistency (для LWT) |\n| CQL | KEYSPACE | Keyspace для запроса |\n| CQL | SIMPLE_KEYSPACE | Single keyspace mode |\n| CQL | PAGE_SIZE | Result page size |\n| CQL | PAGING_STATE | Paging state token |\n\n---\n\n## 3. Рекомендации к критериям приёмки\n\n| # | КОГДА | ТОГДА |\n|---|-------|-------|\n| 1 | Клиент отправляет INSERT на port 9042 | Данные записаны в MemTable, CommitLog, возвращено Ok |\n| 2 | SELECT с WHERE partition_key | Данные прочитаны из MemTable + SSTable, bloom filter applied |\n| 3 | INSERT ... IF NOT EXISTS (Paxos) | Кворум подтверждён, данные зафиксированы |\n| 4 | Реплика down при записи | Hints сохранены, replay при восстановлении |\n| 5 | Read repair | Дивергентные реплики синхронизированы |\n| 6 | Node bootstrap | Данные стримятся с существующих узлов |\n| 7 | Compaction (STCS/LCS/TWCS) | SSTable объединены, tombstone удалены |\n| 8 | Node failure | Gossiper детектирует (phi threshold), failure detector срабатывает |\n| 9 | Consistency QUORUM | Запись/чтение ожидает (RF/2)+1 реплик |\n| 10 | CDC enabled | Изменения пишутся в CDC table |\n| 11 | nodetool repair | Anti-entropy repair синхронизирует реплики |\n| 12 | nodetool flush | MemTable flush к SSTable |\n| 13 | nodetool compaction | Ручной запуск compaction |\n| 14 | CREATE KEYSPACE с NTS | Реплики созданы согласно DC |\n| 15 | ALTER TABLE compaction | Стратегия изменена |\n| 16 | TRUNCATE table | Все данные удалены |\n| 17 | DROP KEYSPACE | Keyspace и данные удалены |\n| 18 | CREATE ROLE | Роль создана в system_auth |\n| 19 | GRANT PERMISSION | Permission выдано |\n| 20 | JMX connect | MBean доступен |\n\n---\n\n## 4. Нефункциональные требования\n\n### 4.1. Безопасность\n\n#### Authentication\n\n| Authenticator | Description |\n|---------------|-------------|\n| AllowAllAuthenticator | No authentication (default) |\n| PasswordAuthenticator | Username/password (system_auth) |\n| MutualTlsAuthenticator | mTLS authentication |\n\n#### Authorization\n\n| Authorizer | Description |\n|------------|-------------|\n| AllowAllAuthorizer | All actions allowed (default) |\n| CassandraAuthorizer | RBAC (system_auth.role_permissions) |\n| CassandraNetworkAuthorizer | Per-DC authorization |\n| CassandraCIDRAuthorizer | CIDR-based authorization |\n\n#### Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)\n\n- **Permissions**: SELECT, MODIFY, CREATE, DROP, AUTHORIZE, ALTER\n- **IRoleManager**: CassandraRoleManager (default)\n- **Role caching**: roles_validity_in_ms\n\n#### Encryption\n\n| Type | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| client_encryption_options | Client-to-node TLS |\n| server_encryption_options | Node-to-node TLS (internode) |\n| Transparent Data Encryption (TDE) | At-rest encryption |\n\n#### Audit\n\n- **AuditLogOptions** — logging CQL queries\n- **Log categories**: DML, DDL, AUTH, READ, WRITE\n- **Storage**: to file or table (system.audit_log)\n\n### 4.2. Производительность\n\n| Параметр | Default | Описание |\n|----------|---------|----------|\n| native_transport_port | 9042 | CQL native port |\n| rpc_port | 9160 | Thrift port |\n| concurrent_reads | 32 | Read threads |\n| concurrent_writes | 32 | Write threads |\n| compaction_throughput_mb_per_sec | 16 | Max compaction MB/s |\n| memtable_heap_space_in_mb | 1/4 heap | MemTable heap size |\n| memtable_offheap_space_in_mb | 1/4 heap | MemTable off-heap |\n| native_transport_receive_queue_size_in_bytes | — | Receive queue size |\n| max_hints_delivery_threads | 2 | Hints delivery threads |\n\n#### Timeouts (ms)\n\n| Parameter | Default |\n|-----------|---------|\n| read_request_timeout_in_ms | 5000 |\n| write_request_timeout_in_ms | 2000 |\n| range_request_timeout_in_ms | 10000 |\n| request_timeout_in_ms | 10000 |\n| counter_write_request_timeout_in_ms | 5000 |\n| cas_contention_timeout_in_ms | 1000 |\n| truncate_request_timeout_in_ms | 60000 |\n\n### 4.3. Надежность\n\n#### Durability\n\n| Parameter | Description |\n|-----------|-------------|\n| commitlog_sync | periodic/batch |\n| commitlog_total_space_in_mb | Total size |\n| commitlog_segment_size_in_mb | Segment size |\n| durable_writes | Per-keyspace durability |\n\n#### Fault Tolerance\n\n- **Hints** — async delivery для offline реплик\n- **Tombstone** — soft deletes с gc_grace_seconds\n- **gc_grace_seconds** — 10 days default (tombstone cleanup)\n- **No single point of failure** — P2P gossip\n\n#### Anti-Entropy Repair\n\n- **nodetool repair** — merkle tree\n- **Incremental repair** — repaired data tracking\n- **Blacklist** — exclude tables/nodes\n\n#### Multi-Datacenter\n\n- **NetworkTopologyStrategy** — per-DC RF\n- **Local consistency** — LOCAL_ONE, LOCAL_QUORUM\n- **Snitch**: GossipingPropertyFileSnitch, Ec2Snitch, etc.\n\n### 4.4. Мониторинг\n\n#### 4.4.1. JMX MBeans\n\n| MBean | Object Name | Description |\n|-------|-------------|-------------|\n| ColumnFamilyStore | org.apache.cassandra.db:type=ColumnFamilyStores | Per-table metrics |\n| StorageProxy | org.apache.cassandra.internal:type=StorageProxy | Cluster-wide metrics |\n| FailureDetector | org.apache.cassandra.gms:type=FailureDetector | Node health |\n| CompactionManager | org.apache.cassandra.db:type=CompactionManager | Compaction ops |\n| CacheService | org.apache.cassandra.service:type=CacheService | Cache metrics |\n| StorageService | org.apache.cassandra.service:type=StorageService | Node operations |\n\n#### 4.4.2. Metrics (CodaHale/Dropwizard)\n\n| Metric Category | Description |\n|----------------|-------------|\n| ClientRequestMetrics | Read/write latency, timeout |\n| TableMetrics | Per-table read/write/compaction |\n| CacheMetrics | Row cache, key cache hit rate |\n| StorageMetrics | Dis